title: Dymocks Melbourne Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Situated within Dymocks Collins Street bookshop. Varied menu range, food is labeled. Has vegan patties, vegan Funky Pies, vegan cupcakes, salads. Decor is open-plan with formica tables and wooden chairs, some padded seating. Small upstairs landing/alcove with couch away from main seating area.
